  <graphic url="https://iiif.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/iiif/image/daa5aba7-c401-42c3-bb9a-100a0a2e2c76"/>
  <zone type="main">
    <line>With blood, &amp; hearts broken by long hope, &amp; love</line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">Slain at</del>
        <add place="superlinear">Dragged to</add>
      </mod> his altars soiled &amp; garlandless</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e3-0078.03"/>
    <line>Flattering the thing they feared, which fear was hate</line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">Stand</del>
        <add place="sublinear">Frown,</add>
      </mod> mouldering fast, <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">on</del>
        <add place="intralinear">oer</add>
      </mod> their abandoned shrines <unclear reason="illegible">—</unclear></line>
    <line>The painted veil by those who were, called life,</line>
    <line>Which mimicked, as with colours idly spread,</line>
    <line>All men believed or hoped, is torn aside—</line>
    <line>The loathsome mask has fallen, the man remains</line>
    <line>Sceptreless, free, uncircumscribed <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">,</del>
        <add place="intralinear"><unclear>:</unclear>—</add>
      </mod> but man <unclear reason="illegible">:</unclear></line>
    <line>Equal, unclassed, tribeless, &amp; nationless</line>
    <line>Exempt from awe <unclear reason="illegible">,</unclear> worship, degree,— the
      King</line>
    <line>Over himself; just, gentle, wise <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">,</del>
        <add place="intralinear"><unclear>:</unclear>—</add>
      </mod>but man:</line>
    <line>Passionless <unclear reason="illegible">?</unclear> no — <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">but</del>
        <add place="superlinear">yet</add>
      </mod> free from guilt or pain</line>
    <line>Which were, for his will made, or suffered them <unclear reason="illegible"
      >,</unclear></line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">Though not</del>
        <add place="superlinear">Nor yet</add>
      </mod> exempt, <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">yet</del>
        <add place="superlinear">though</add>
      </mod> ruling them like slaves,</line>
    <line>From chance &amp; death &amp; mutability</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">Which</del>
      <del rend="strikethrough"><mod>
          <del rend="overwritten">T</del>
          <add place="intralinear">W</add>
      </mod>hich clog that spirit, else which might <add place="sublinear"><del rend="strikethrough">outsoar</del></add></del></line>
    <anchor xml:id="e3-0078.04"/>
    <line>The loftiest star of unascended Heaven</line>
    <line>Pinnacled dim in the intense inane.</line>
    <line><add><metamark function="count">1915</metamark></add></line>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e3-0078.02"/>
    <line rend="center">Prometheus</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e3-0078.02"/>
